					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Alright, some Thank You’s right off the bat:</p> <p>Obviously, shoutout to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tygently" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2038009&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1592713735" alt="TyGently" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2038009)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tygently" >TyGently</a></span> for writing the first half of this; I doubt it was anywhere close to where you expected for it to go, but I hope I wrote something we can both enjoy.</p> <p>Thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/its-a-bad-idea" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3181609&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1592713735" alt="Its a Bad Idea" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3181609)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/its-a-bad-idea" >Its a Bad Idea</a></span> for critting the first thing I’ve ever written for the wiki, and being the only person to answer my plea for crit in the SCPD discord. (I’m not bitter, not one bit)</p> <p>Big shouts to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/niblic" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1802367&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1592713735" alt="Niblic" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1802367)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/niblic" >Niblic</a></span> for helping me with the 3D modeling work, even if I didn't end up using it.</p> <p>Thanks to my critters, obviously: <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/roget" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1229263&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1592713735" alt="Roget" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1229263)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/roget" >Roget</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/karakatt" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5950867&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1592713735" alt="KaraKatt" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5950867)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/karakatt" >KaraKatt</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/naveil" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5986482&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1592713735" alt="Naveil" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5986482)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/naveil" >Naveil</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/chiifu" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6394107&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1592713735" alt="chiifu" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6394107)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/chiifu" >chiifu</a></span>, and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/placeholder-mcd" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6536693&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1592713735" alt="Placeholder McD" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6536693)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/placeholder-mcd" >Placeholder McD</a></span>. All of you gave me invaluable feedback, and I wouldn’t have had this if you didn’t stand by me.</p> <p>Also, apologies to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zyn" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1404533&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1592713735" alt="Zyn" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1404533)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zyn" >Zyn</a></span> for fucking up the Crit forums and taking time out of her day</p> <p>Credit to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/luxaiko" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5963620&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1592713735" alt="Luxaiko" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5963620)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/luxaiko" >Luxaiko</a></span> for keeping me positive and also giving me help with wording stuff, as well as for being cool as h*ck</p> <p>And the <em>most</em> thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/deadly-bread" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3988532&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1592713735" alt="Deadly Bread" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3988532)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/deadly-bread" >Deadly Bread</a></span> for giving me advice, ideas, critique, and unwavering support throughout this process. We’ve been closer than a Single Live Bee and Cleopatra’s Lack of a Corpse. I love ya, buddy.</p> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;Image&nbsp;Sources&nbsp;and&nbsp;References</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">–&nbsp;Close</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <p>Dante Quote I bastardized for Hermes</p> <blockquote> <p>We once were men and now are arid stumps:<br /> your hand might well have shown us greater mercy<br /> had we been nothing more than souls of serpents.</p> </blockquote> <p>Image links:<br /> <a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Winter_2004_DreamHack_LAN_Party.jpg">https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Winter_2004_DreamHack_LAN_Party.jpg</a></p> <p><a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/Category:Games_Convention_2006#/media/File:World_Cyber_Games_(2671291701).jpg">https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/Category:Games_Convention_2006#/media/File:World_Cyber_Games_(2671291701).jpg</a></p> <p><a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/Category:Hermes_bearing_the_child_Dionysos#/media/File:Hermes_di_Prassitele,_at_Olimpia,_front_2.jpg">https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/Category:Hermes_bearing_the_child_Dionysos#/media/File:Hermes_di_Prassitele,_at_Olimpia,_front_2.jpg</a></p> </div> </div> </div> 
